data.description: This is a beautiful property with an excellent opportunity for investment. This 2 unit home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms downstairs, with a 1 bed/1 bath seperate unit upstairs. You can supplement your mortgage by living in one, and renting the other. The home has been very tastefully redone with refinished hardwoods, new kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite counters, interior laundry, custom built ins, and a master with its own entry off of its own charming and private courtyard.
data.whatILove: Has a fully contained 1/1 apartment with its own entrance to supplement the mortgage.
